content.p: Explore our beautiful campuses and make the most of our spaces with our useful campus maps, including University Park campus, Jubilee campus, along with many more that are accessible via the Campus maps and floor plans link. Our maps help you quickly find your way around. You can find lecture theatres, bus stops and our Student Service Centres. If you're visiting us on an open day, our web pages also help you get to Nottingham, whether you're travelling by train, tram, bus or plane. Campus maps Student Services centres Our campus maps and floor plans of the University buildings are available online.
